{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_mian_tan_lao_ban","speaker_name":"面摊老板","listener":null,"text":"客官，来点什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"来一大碗牛肉面。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":42,"line_end":42},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"马上来，要不要切点卤菜，温一壶酒？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":46,"line_end":46},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"不必，面里加两个卤蛋就够了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":48,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_niu_rou_tang","speaker_name":"牛肉汤","listener":null,"text":"你怎么喝起别人煮的牛肉汤来了呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_niu_rou_tang","speaker_name":"牛肉汤","listener":null,"text":"你不喜欢喝我煮的牛肉汤吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_mian_tan_lao_ban","speaker_name":"面摊老板","listener":null,"text":"温一壶女儿红来。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"来，干一杯。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":80,"line_end":80},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"为什么要干杯？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":82,"line_end":82},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"猫捉到老鼠，总是要调侃一番，现在猫儿叫老鼠喝酒，老鼠会不听话吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":84,"line_end":84},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"好酒！","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":88,"line_end":88},{"speaker":"char_niu_rou_tang","speaker_name":"牛肉汤","listener":null,"text":"比我的牛肉汤好吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":90,"line_end":90},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"那是不能比的。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":92,"line_end":92},{"speaker":"char_niu_rou_tang","speaker_name":"牛肉汤","listener":null,"text":"为什么不能比？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"猫跟老鼠能比吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_niu_rou_tang","speaker_name":"牛肉汤","listener":null,"text":"你是说，猫要喝好酒，老鼠要喝汤，所以不能比？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":98,"line_end":98}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_lu_xiao_feng","name":"陆小凤","alias":[],"identity":"江湖侠客","faction":"","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"","one_line":"四条眉毛的江湖奇人，轻功了得","personality":{"traits":["机智","幽默","重情义","洒脱","机敏"],"speech_style":"幽默诙谐","temperament":"洒脱"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"text":"第十八回　猫捉老鼠\n假如猫和老鼠比赛跑步，谁跑得最快？\n\n陆小凤飞奔的时候，忽然想起这个问题。\n\n应该是猫跑得快吧？陆小凤想，但是，老鼠能一头钻进洞里，也可以一冲就躲到阴沟里，这绝对是猫做不到的事情。..."}]},{"id":"char_gong_jiu","name":"宫九","alias":[],"identity":"神秘追踪者","faction":"","role":"villain","archetype":"villain","rank":"","one_line":"神秘的追踪者，与陆小凤为敌","personality":{"traits":["阴险","狡诈","有钱","执着","冷酷"],"speech_style":"阴沉","temperament":"阴险"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"text":"第十八回　猫捉老鼠\n假如猫和老鼠比赛跑步，谁跑得最快？\n\n陆小凤飞奔的时候，忽然想起这个问题。\n\n应该是猫跑得快吧？陆小凤想，但是，老鼠能一头钻进洞里，也可以一冲就躲到阴沟里，这绝对是猫做不到的事情。..."}]},{"id":"char_niu_rou_tang","name":"牛肉汤","alias":[],"identity":"宫九的同伴","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"npc","rank":"","one_line":"宫九身边的女子，擅长烹饪","personality":{"traits":["温柔","顺从","美丽","机灵","神秘"],"speech_style":"甜美","temperament":"温柔"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[18],"source_refs":[{"chapter":18,"line_start":1,"line_end":100,"text":"第十八回　猫捉老鼠\n假如猫和老鼠比赛跑步，谁跑得最快？\n\n陆小凤飞奔的时候，忽然想起这个问题。\n\n应该是猫跑得快吧？陆小凤想，但是，老鼠能一头钻进洞里，也可以一冲就躲到阴沟里，这绝对是猫做不到的事情。..."}]},{"id":"char_mian_tan_lao_ban","name":"面摊老板","alias":[],"identity":"面摊老板","faction":"","role":"npc","archetype":"npc"