{"segment":2,"line_start":101,"line_end":200,"dialogues":[{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"猫可以坐车，老鼠却要走路，猫可以在车上睡觉，老鼠却要强撑精神赶路，能比吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":102,"line_end":102},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"好词，你们能编出这么好的词，为什么不去做一件事？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":106,"line_end":106},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"什么事？","tone":"微笑","chapter":18,"line_start":108,"line_end":108},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"相声。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":110,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"我实在很佩服你。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":114,"line_end":114},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"为什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":116,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"因为你这个时候还有心情说笑话。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":118,"line_end":118},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"这也许是老鼠自得其乐的方法吧。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":120,"line_end":120},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"那你自己去乐吧。","tone":"淡然","chapter":18,"line_start":122,"line_end":122},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"你要赶我走？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":124,"line_end":124},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"你不是要逃开我吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"我能不能问你一个问题再走？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"什么问题？","tone":"疑问","chapter":18,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"我很想知道，你怎么会追到这里？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"很简单，只有一个字。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":134,"line_end":134},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"一个字？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":136,"line_end":136},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"不错，一个字。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":138,"line_end":138},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"什么字？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":140,"line_end":140},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"钱。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":142,"line_end":142},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"钱？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":144,"line_end":144},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"有钱能使鬼推磨，何况是人？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":146,"line_end":146},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"你买通了人来跟踪我？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":148,"line_end":148},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"不对。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":150,"line_end":150},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"为什么不对？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":152,"line_end":152},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"连我都追不上你，世上还有谁能追得上你？就算有，这种人能用钱收买吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":154,"line_end":154},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"所以我才不懂，你就算花钱买人，也不应该知道我的去处。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":156,"line_end":156},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"我花钱买的人，不是一个，而是很多个。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":158,"line_end":158},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"很多个？有多少？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":160,"line_end":160},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"我也不知道有多少。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"你很想知道其中奥妙吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":168,"line_end":168},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"你不愿意讲，我也不勉强。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":170,"line_end":170},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"这是什么记号？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":176,"line_end":176},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"这表示陆小凤在此。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":178,"line_end":178},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"哦？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":180,"line_end":180},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"你知道我喝这壶酒要花多少钱吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":182,"line_end":182},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"花多少钱？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":184,"line_end":184},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"你明白了吗？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":190,"line_end":190},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"明白了一半。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":192,"line_end":192},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"我再跟你说吧，我已经放出话去，只要看到一个脸上有四条眉毛的人走过，就做个箭号指示方向，看到四条眉毛的人歇息或用饭，就做个三角形记号，我看到这些记号，就有重赏，你想想，你能走到哪里去？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":194,"line_end":194},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":null,"listener":null,"text":"最好把真的眉毛剃掉，就没有人认得你了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":200,"line_end":200}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":201,"line_end":300,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"你笑什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":206,"line_end":206},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"我笑自己，实在太傻。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":208,"line_end":208},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"为什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":210,"line_end":210},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"既然走不了，我为什么还要走？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":212,"line_end":212},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"你不走？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":214,"line_end":214},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"我不走了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":216,"line_end":216},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"其实，你不走我也不反对，只是……","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":218,"line_end":218},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"只是什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":222,"line_end":222},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"我在这里陪你不打紧，我有醇酒，又有美人，你呢？沙曼呢？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":224,"line_end":224},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"你去哪里？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":230,"line_end":230},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"睡觉去。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":232,"line_end":232},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"你要干什么？","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":236,"line_end":236},{"speaker":"char_lu_xiao_feng","speaker_name":"陆小凤","listener":null,"text":"我要黄金。","tone":"陈述","chapter":18,"line_start":238,"line_end":238},{"speaker":"char_gong_jiu","speaker_name":"宫九","listener":null,"text":"我为什么要把黄金给你？","tone":"陈述